              <p>&gt; [2026-01-15] <span class="text-[var(--accent)]">V-JEPA 2</span> released by Meta. "World Model" physics simulation achieved.</p>
              <p>&gt; [2026-02-02] <span class="text-[var(--accent)]">UBTech Walker S2</span> autonomous battery change confirmed at Zeekr factory.</p>
